narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, it's more difficult than L2 (obviously) but it focuses a lot on literature/film, which is enjoyable. It helped improve my reading comprehension. Take it with Professor Alexandrov. She's lively and overall a really cool professor.
Take it if you want to improve your spanish!
this is probably for a language requirement..soooo yea.

It's a fine class itself as a level 3 grammar and vocab learning class. Homework every night, but not that much. Sybil Alexandrov is phenomenal, enthusiastic, helpful and kind. Definitely don't miss the opportunity to take a class with her.
yes, definitely...especially if you want to become fluent
It is a good amount of work but all of it is necessary. If you must take it then you should and keep up with all of the work.
